node.text: We are keeping our Mutual Aid efforts going by distributing funds directly to individuals and organizations supporting the empowerment, and safety of the Black Community. We will also be organizing relief efforts focused on providing groceries and home cooked meals to Black people throughout Los Angeles. We will rebuild and heal together! Stay safe, and stay strong! #BLACKLIVESMATTER

A huge thanks to the @nourishably team for collaborating with us on this project! STAY SAFE. BLACK LIVES MATTER.

node.text: In honour of #FOODNOTRENT , we‚Äôre providing meals to QTIPOC‚ÄôS who may have a limited or no supply of food. This pandemic has put a lot of us out of work, and made life even more difficult for those who already had economic pressures. Including the elderly and homeless population. This is our way of also honouring the mutual aids that have been working harder than the government to ensure the safety of the people. FILL OUT THE FORM IN OUR BIO, SEND US A DM OR EMAIL NOISYLIBRARY53@GMAIL.COM BEFORE OR ON MAY 8TH TO LET US KNOW IF YOU OR ANYONE YOU KNOW MAY NEED THIS OFFERING.
